      <title>高通与英特尔接洽商谈收购事宜：华尔街日报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-20/qualcomm-approached-intel-about-a-takeover-wsj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，高通最近几天向竞争对手英特尔提出了收购要约。对于英特尔来说，这笔交易将是一笔巨大的交易，而且正值这家芯片制造商遭遇其五十年历史上最严重的危机之一之际。Ed Ludlow 在“Bloomberg The Close”中详细介绍了此事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-20/qualcomm-approached-intel-about-a-takeover-wsj</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 20:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zoom 将削减股票薪酬，加入 Salesforce 和 Workday 的行列</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/zoom-to-reduce-stock-based-compensation-joining-salesforce-workday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Zoom Video Communications Inc. 正在减少使用公司股票向员工支付薪酬的做法，加入 Salesforce Inc. 和 Workday Inc. 等同行的行列，减少对科技行业常见薪酬技术的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/zoom-to-reduce-stock-based-compensation-joining-salesforce-workday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 20:09:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果 iPhone 上市，微软需要人工智能助力 | 彭博科技</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-20/apple-s-iphone-hits-stores-microsoft-s-ai-power-needs-bloomberg-technology</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的 Caroline Hyde 和 Ed Ludlow 分析了苹果 iPhone 16 的销量，该产品今天上市，但没有关键的 AI 功能。此外，微软对 AI 能力的需求促使休眠反应堆复活，我们听到了 Salesforce 首席执行官马克·贝尼奥夫和该公司风险投资主管的讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-20/apple-s-iphone-hits-stores-microsoft-s-ai-power-needs-bloomberg-technology</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 20:00:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>有报道称高通正在寻求收购，英特尔股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/intel-gains-on-report-that-qualcomm-made-takeover-approach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《华尔街日报》报道高通公司就收购事宜与英特尔公司接洽后，英特尔公司股价上涨，这可能创下芯片行业的最高纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/intel-gains-on-report-that-qualcomm-made-takeover-approach</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 19:27:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ION 在搁置 8 月单独交易后重新定价杠杆贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/ion-reprices-leveraged-loan-after-shelving-separate-august-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ION Analytics 于上周五扩大并重新定价了一笔杠杆贷款的规模。在 8 月初全球市场动荡之后，不到一个月的时间，该公司刚刚取消了对另一笔杠杆贷款的类似举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/ion-reprices-leveraged-loan-after-shelving-separate-august-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 19:09:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谷歌如何垄断广告技术市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/how-google-allegedly-monopolized-the-ad-technology-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部在联邦反垄断审判中指控，谷歌通过限制或消除其客户（包括网站出版商和广告商）的选择，垄断了用于购买和销售在线展示广告的技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/how-google-allegedly-monopolized-the-ad-technology-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 18:50:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Sandvine 将退出数十个国家，并更换首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/sandvine-to-exit-dozens-of-countries-replace-ceo-in-overhaul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科技公司 Sandvine 宣布彻底改革其商业模式并更换领导层，此前该公司多年来一直因向专制政府销售产品而饱受批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-20/sandvine-to-exit-dozens-of-countries-replace-ceo-in-overhaul</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Sep 2024 14:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
